| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1140 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a725cc9-83b6-50b4-9f05-6f1335d434bb"
